播放”，这些名字还将包括“暂停”，“快进”，“倒带”和“停止”  - 他说他18岁时就说了这个想法。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/awbaFPhoACA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-writes-open-letter-urging-uk-government-to-invest-in-music-education-3848492">向英国政府写了一封公开信，呼吁立即和长期资助音乐教育。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-builds-the-old-phone-pub-named-after-new-song-in-ipswich-usa-and-shows-up-to-perform-chappell-roan-cover-3850870">Ed Sheeran帖子建立了以新歌在美国伊普斯维奇（Ipswich）的新歌命名的旧手机酒吧，并出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现Chappell Roan Cover。</p> ;
